Package eplimited.osea.classification

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BDACParameters
    Beat detection and classification parameter definitions.
    BeatAnalyzer
    This file contains functions for determining the QRS onset, QRS offset, beat onset, beat offset, polarity, and isoelectric level for a beat.
    BeatDetectionAndClassification
    BDAC contains functions for handling Beat Detection And Classification.
    Classifier
    Classify.cpp contains functions for classifying beats.
    ECGCODES  
    Matcher
    Match beats to previous beats.
    NoiseChecker
    This file contains functions for evaluating the noise content of a beat.
    PostClassifier
    This file contains functions for classifying beats based after the following beat is detected.
    RythmChecker
    Rythmchk.cpp contains functions for classifying RR intervals as either NORMAL, PVC, or UNKNOWN.
